OL,6,FThe National Minimum Wage is also set
OL,7,Fto rise from #8.60 to #10.00 an hour
OL,8,Ffor 18 to 20 year old's - a much
OL,9,Fchunkier (16%) step towards Labour's
OL,10,Fmanifesto pledge to create a single
OL,11,Fadult rate.
OL,13,F"The government is delivering on its
OL,14,Fpromise to make work pay," applauds
OL,15,Fthe Trades Union Congress.
OL,17,FThe business lobby group is less
OL,18,Fenthusiastic.
