OL,6,FThe trick here is to strike a balance
OL,7,Fbetween raising the living standards
OL,8,Fof the lowest paid workers in the UK
OL,9,Fwithout sacrificing significant
OL,10,Fnumbers of jobs.
OL,12,FFor much of the last ten years, the
OL,13,FNational Living Wage has consistently
OL,14,Frisen by more than average hourly pay.
