OL,6,FIn 2015, the then Chancellor, George
OL,7,FOsborne, set a target for it to reach
OL,8,F60% of median earnings by 2020.
OL,10,FIn 2019, one of his successors, Sajid
OL,11,FJavid, increased the target to 66.7%
OL,12,Fby 2024.
OL,14,FAccording to the Resolution
OL,15,FFoundation, Javid's target has been
OL,16,Fhit and today's decision will keep it
OL,17,Fat that level.
OL,19,FCould the government have been more
OL,20,Fambitious?
