OL,6,FThe Resolution Foundation thinks not,
OL,7,Fnot least as the chancellor is
OL,8,Fexpected to increase the rate of
OL,9,Fnational insurance contributions for
OL,10,Femployers in tomorrow's budget and
OL,11,Flower the threshold above which the
OL,12,Ftax is paid.
OL,14,FSaddling businesses with higher costs
OL,15,Finevitably affects employment but
OL,16,Funtil now the evidence suggests the
OL,17,Fnegative impact has been limited.
