OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHowever there is a "tipping point,"
OL,12,Fbeyond which increases to the minimum
OL,13,Fwage begin to cost higher numbers of
OL,14,Fjobs or damage productivity.
OL,16,FThe Low Pay Commission estimates that
OL,17,Fhalf of all the jobs paying at or
OL,18,Fbelow the minimum wage are in retail,
OL,19,Fhospitality, cleaning and maintenance.
